Bug Status
Date:		January 12, 1999



*****
Bug 1: Premature Completion of ODStringDemo

If ODActor.getCurrent() consists of:

    public double getCurrentTime() {
        if( _rcvrTimeTable.size() == 0 ) {
            return _currentTime;
        }
        RcvrTimeTriple triple = (RcvrTimeTriple)_rcvrTimeTable.first();
        _currentTime = triple.getTime();
        return _currentTime;
    }

Then ODStringDemo reaches 
	a	13.5
	i	14.0
	n	5000.0
	;	5000.0
and the queue size = 2 (see ODPrintString.wrapup). This assumes 
completionTime = 5001.


If ODActor.getCurrent() consists of:

    public double getCurrentTime() {
        return _currentTime;
    }

Then ODStringDemo reaches 
	O	10.0
	D	10.5
	_	11.0
	;	11.5
and the queue size = 8 (see ODPrintString.wrapup). This assumes 
completionTime = 5001.

